de.hsa.jam
Class ControllerEngine

java.lang.Object
  de.hsa.jam.AbstractController
      de.hsa.jam.ControllerEngine
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.util.EventListener
public class ControllerEngine
extends AbstractController

This class implements the controller. The controller translates user actions into Property Updates on the Model.
If the Model fires a Property Change the controller translates this action into a Component Update.

Author:
Michael Wager
